      <title>Bunds擦除了历史性的下降，因为飞往安全的航班减轻了债务成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bunds-erase-historic-drop-as-flight-to-safety-eases-debt-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）广泛的关税宣布之后，投资者寻求该地区最安全的债务，德国的债券集会了，消除了上个月借贷成本的历史性激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bunds-erase-historic-drop-as-flight-to-safety-eases-debt-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:17:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
